description:
Brooke and Danielle get together IRL for their last chat 2021!!  The gals discuss what’s been new in their lives, their santacon experiences + some celebrity encounters.  Brooke and Danielle also share thoughts on  “And Just Like That” and the PR moves surrounding the new show.  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories on Instagram!
